        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer596573115" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8955982879480711822">With a compelling premise and an electric start, Shelia Dalton’s The Girl in the Box, is a great read. Dalton skillfully examines the complexities of perception as her protagonist embarks on a journey for the truth about her husband’s death. As insightful as thrilling, Dalton’s smooth writing made this a one-sitting read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


